y fabulous cocktails at Tonic Poolside Bar & Grille. Relax, unwind and revitalize your soul at our beautifully designed Rock Spa®. Offering an array of enticing treatment options, Rock Spa® puts a rock spin on traditional treatments in a modern Zen setting. And during your stay, you’ll also get to enjoy legendary live band performances, customized playlists and guitar jam sessions in your room with Sound of Your Stay®. So check-in and get ready to feel like a rock star and live the Rock n\' Roll life!', 'Good', 5, '★★★★★', '★★★★', '★★★★★', '★★★★'),
