 Margao Railway Station the resort is ideally located for a relaxing and fun filled Vacation in Goa. Our 203 rooms and suites offer comfort and serenity combined with modern amenities with an option of a garden view pool view or sea view with attached balconies. When travelling for a family retreat take advantage of the game room kids playground and activity zone or just unwind at the outdoor pool and revitalize at the Spa Villa offering multiple ayurvedic treatments.Experience a choice of Indian and International cuisines at Mardi Gras Our 24 hour Coffee shop. Rediscover the ethnic flavors of the Far East at the exquisite Whispers of the Orient or try out our wood fired pizzas at the Mediterranean restaurant Fig and Olive. The lobby level bar Sun Downer offers a relaxing view of the Goan sunset or have an exciting evening at our beach side restaurant Beach Grill offering a huge selection of freshly caught fish cooked to perfection. Organize your special wedding day, corporate retreats or productive meetings at the Holiday Inn Resort Goa, offering the largest ballroom at 5065 sq ft and able to accommodate up to 800 guests.', 'Excellent', 5, '★★★★★', '★★★★', '★★★★★', '★★★★'),
(38, 2, 'Hilton Jaipur', 'Grand Geejgarh, 42, Hawa Sadak, Jaipur, Rajasthan 302006', '<iframe src=\"https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d3558.06880178917!2d75.78165911496991!3d26.90131148313259!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x396db41343ba45c1%3A0x6c886175dc6cde79!2sHilton%20Jaipur!5e0!3m2!1sen!2sin!4v1648280760605!5m2!1sen!2sin\" width=\"600\" height=\"450\" style=\"border:0;\" allowfullscreen=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer-when-downgrade\"></iframe>', 0, 'Hilton Jaipur is just 2 miles from the Jaipur trai...', 0, '★★★★★', 0, 5050, 'https://www.booking.com/searchresults.en-gb.html?ss=Hilton+Jaipur%2C+Jaipur%2C+Rajasthan%2C+India&ssne=Jaipur&ssne_untouched=Jaipur&label=msn-LOcHQGfA16aswDjFb7_rcw-80539252256335%3Atikwd-80539278535451%3Aloc-90%3Aneo%3Amte%3Alp155345%3Adec%3Aqsbooking+.com&sid=d58189f861dd5b31e3eb9889d5648e3b&aid=375653&lang=en-gb&sb=1&src_elem=sb&src=searchresults&dest_id=1039091&dest_type=hotel&ac_position=0&ac_click_type=b&ac_langcode=en&ac_suggestion_list_length=2&search_selected=true&search_pageview_id=d8b349c2934a022c&checkin=2022-04-21&checkout=2022-04-22&group_adults=2&no_rooms=1&group_children=0&sb_travel_purpose=leisure', 5540, 'https://us.trip.com/hotels/list?city=3288&countryId=107&checkin=2022/03/17&checkout=2022/03/18&highPrice=-1&optionId=2198945&optionType=Hotel&directSearch=0&optionName=Hilton%20Jaipur&display=Hilton%20Jaipur&crn=1&adult=1&children=0&searchBoxArg=t&travelPurpose=0&ctm_ref=ix_sb_dl&domestic=0', 0, 'Ideally located in the heart of the city, Hilton Jaipur is just 2 miles from the Jaipur train station and from major tourist attractions, popular shopping destinations, and prime business hubs. Featuring 179 spacious rooms with four eclectic dining options including Aurum- global cuisine restaurant, Chaandi- the Indian kitchen, Krystal- the high energy bar and Signature- the rooftop lounge. The hotel offers 24 hours front desk assistance, Wi-Fi, currency exchange service, laundry with dry cleaning, luggage storage, free parking and spacious rooms with bathtub, hairdryer, and free toiletries. Zivaya spa, well-equipped fitness center, and outdoor swimming create enormous options to break away from a hectic routine. Spread across 10,000 sq. ft, Hilton Jaipur provides excellent venues for all social and business purposes that can accommodate up to 700 guests. There’s no better place to give your kid an amazing vacation experience while having fun than here at Hilton Jaipur.', 'Very Good', 5, '★★★★★', '★★★★', '★★★★★', '★★★★'),
